{"tid":443995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"42歲男唔開心菜刀自宮 女友大驚報警 ","createTime":"2017-10-22T06:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T09:10:08.000Z","uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e586f9dbd6d17dd815d044d73c962dbe10fdaf09","tid":443995,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171022/large/1508644673_5f1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171022%2Flarge%2F1508644673_5f1c.jpg&h=9df7a3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晨7時許，柴灣愛民街30號一大廈樓上單位，42歲菲律賓籍男子MARTIN ，報稱自己不開心，揮動菜刀將「子孫根」分體，其37歲女友返回寓所，發現男友下體淌血，大驚失色，慌忙為男友清理血迹，一名男鄰居見狀報警求助，救護員到場將菲漢送院救治。警方到場調查，將案件列企圖自殺處理，正了解事主自殺原因。<br />\n<br />\n近年自宮男事件簿<br />\n2011年6月21日<br />\n34歲男子在黃大仙寓所疑吸食冰毒後失去常性，手執利剪在住所梯間自宮，將陰莖一剪而下，他事後把血淋淋的陰莖放在走廊消防喉轆位置，然後負傷回家。救護員接報到場將他送往手術室進行接駁陰莖手術，最後接駁手術成功完成<br />\n<br />\n2010年1月29日<br />\n24歲泰國籍男子受感情困擾，在機場登機前於食肆偷走一把牛肉刀，躲在廁格內自割陰莖<br />\n<br />\n2005年7月27日<br />\n47歲男子躲在灣仔堅拿道女廁，自稱厭倦做男人，用利剪自剪陰莖大量出血，事後送院治理<br />\n<br />\n2004年3月8日<br />\n48歲內地男子不堪女友分手打擊，03年11月自宮接駁康復後，再在旺角塘尾道租住房間內揮剪刀自剪下體，並將睾丸吞下，事後送院治療<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"d525a45fb934866026b1d37c261ea9cfa053db22","tid":443995,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57362371&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57362371%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171022&d=9JwYeKXHddSTeQeS7%2B%2BYkb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=48fe0797\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57362371%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171022&h=589a8a4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57362371&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171022</a>"},{"pid":"2bcafdf7231167a853e67329493bfd49347f0e77","tid":443995,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"在旺角塘尾道租住房間內揮剪刀自剪下體，並將睾丸吞下，事後送院治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4db00e6ffbfdd7a034b743e01c638f8bed9ca1d","tid":443995,"uid":33459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"仲忍到痛吞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e213c0385abbaee1b13fbc925c08cb361c1293","tid":443995,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"女友用架條野<br />\n使出軌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9583e618f3d0e77ddb1415d9a99a045fd346af2","tid":443995,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T08:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在旺角塘尾道租住房間內揮剪刀自剪下體，並將睾丸吞下，事後送院治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人間最痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afc453b4feb9dda8bad52b4627275394c14a406","tid":443995,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}